msgid "ElectionEvaluator"
msgstr "ElectionEvaluator"

#: ipres.election_evaluator:1 of
msgid ""
"Election evaluator: computes seat distribution, constituency allocation, "
"and final results."
msgstr ""
"Wahlauswertung: berechnet Sitzverteilung, Wahlkreiszuweisung und "
"Endergebnisse."

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:1 of
msgid "Evaluates a finished election to compute results."
msgstr "Wertet eine abgeschlossene Wahl aus und berechnet die Ergebnisse."

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:3 of
msgid "Orchestrates three evaluation steps in sequence:"
msgstr "Koordiniert drei Auswertungsschritte in Folge:"

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:5 of
msgid ""
":class:`~ipres.seat_distributor.SeatDistributor` ‚Äî distributes "
"parliamentary seats."
msgstr ""
":class:`~ipres.seat_distributor.SeatDistributor` ‚Äî verteilt "
"Parlamentssitze."

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:6 of
msgid ""
":class:`~ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer`"
" ‚Äî determines how many constituencies each party receives."
msgstr ""
":class:`~ipres.constituency_count_determiner.ConstituencyCountDeterminer`"
" ‚Äî bestimmt, wie viele Wahlkreise jede Partei erh√§lt."

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:8 of
msgid ""
":class:`~ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner` ‚Äî assigns "
"specific constituencies to parties by relative importance."
msgstr ""
":class:`~ipres.constituency_assigner.ConstituencyAssigner` ‚Äî weist "
"Parteien konkrete Wahlkreise nach relativer Bedeutung zu."

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:11 of
msgid "Each step can also be instantiated and called independently."
msgstr "Jeder Schritt kann auch eigenst√§ndig instanziiert und aufgerufen werden."

#: ipres.election_evaluator.ElectionEvaluator:13 of
msgid ""
"``constituency_representation`` and evaluation strategy defaults "
"(``seat_distribution_method``, ``quota_correction_strategy``, "
"``constituency_allocation_method``) are derived automatically from "
"``election.electionConfig`` when the corresponding field is ``None`` (the"
" default). Set a field to a non-``None`` value to override the election-"
"level default for a specific evaluation."
msgstr ""
"``constituency_representation`` und die Standardwerte der "
"Auswertungsstrategie (``seat_distribution_method``, "
"``quota_correction_strategy``, ``constituency_allocation_method``) werden "
"automatisch aus ``election.electionConfig`` abgeleitet, wenn das "
"entsprechende Feld ``None`` ist (Standard). Um den wahlweiten Standard f√ºr "
"eine bestimmte Auswertung zu √ºberschreiben, kann ein Feld auf einen "
"Nicht-``None``-Wert gesetzt werden."

